<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037791" n="1"/>
  <opener><lb/><salute>Viro Illustrissimo atque Doctissimo
      <lb/><rs type="person">Johanni Checcotio</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">N. B.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quas pro humanissima tua <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> superioribus diebus propter
  <lb/>adversam valetudinem persolvere nequivi gratias, eas tibi, Vir
  <lb/>Eruditissime, nunc demum, sed m<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>stissima mente, persolvo.
  <pb facs="1037793" n="2"/>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del>Ingenti certe tristitia <add>me</add> affec<del>[...]</del><add>erat</add> nuntius de pericu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>loso <del>[...]</del><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156361761">Fratris</rs> <del>[...]</del>tui statu; sed ex q<del>[...]</del><add>uo</add> multo infaustio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Rev.</abbr> Patre <del>[...]</del><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089921608">Catharino Zeno</rs> accepi nuntium de ipsa
  <lb/>Viri honestissimi morte, dolore pen<del>[...]</del><add>e</add> conficior.<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>Etenim n</add>on possum non graviter ferre jacturam
  <lb/>amici, <del>[...]</del>quem mei studiosum
  <lb/>fuisse, non solum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unibus <rs type="person">amicis</rs>, sed <add>etiam</add> ex ipsius hu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>manissimis ad me <rs type="letter">litteris</rs> satis superque intellexi. Et eo quidem
  <lb/>gravius fero hanc jacturam, quo<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del>majorem animo<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del>ejus convalescentia,
  <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>et de amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> recens inter nos nat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fructibus spem conceperam.</add> Cum igitur tam brevi temporis spatio, quo amicitia inter nos
  <lb/>coaluit, ejus erga me benevolentiam demereri nullo pacto
  <lb/>potuerim, hoc mihi reliquum manet, ut tibi persuadeam, me
  <lb/><del>[...]</del>tanti amici et tam eximii rerum Mathematicarum
  <lb/>cultoris memoriam grata mente culturum.<del>[...]</del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del>
  <lb/>Interim ne justo dolori nimium indulgeas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, sed <add>in</add> Dei voluntat<del>[...]</del><add>e</add>
  <lb/>acquiescas <del>[...]</del><add>qui</add> solatio suo luctum vestrum moderetur, et calami<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tatem hanc alia felicitate compenset! Quod superest gratias
  <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>ago</add> pro enixa tua in me voluntate, rogoque ut eam deme<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rendi, et meam vicissim erga te observantiam demonstrandi
  <lb/>occasionem <add>mihi</add> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>beas. </p> <closer><salute>Vale. </salute><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Venetiis</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-07-14">14. Julii 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
